  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hell Shooter</strong> is a roguelike dungeon crawler game. It features unique attack methods, exhilarating action, an oriental hellish atmosphere, and each character's storytelling.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique attack method</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/2eb5d15d29ce89807a39ff7d5163bd15.poster.avif?t=1756972850\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/2eb5d15d29ce89807a39ff7d5163bd15.webm?t=1756972850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/2eb5d15d29ce89807a39ff7d5163bd15.mp4?t=1756972850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When attacking enemies, you must only attack them by dashing!! Design the optimal attack path by bouncing between structures and enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Soul Eruption</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/96190dee2a2cf793494375854d8ddde2.poster.avif?t=1756972850\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/96190dee2a2cf793494375854d8ddde2.webm?t=1756972850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/96190dee2a2cf793494375854d8ddde2.mp4?t=1756972850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are rewards for good play. Collect the combo gauge to erupt your soul. It will be a powerful attack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >100 items</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/2776a094ce0339303de01981cce9f606.poster.avif?t=1756972850\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/2776a094ce0339303de01981cce9f606.webm?t=1756972850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/2776a094ce0339303de01981cce9f606.mp4?t=1756972850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Countless items will help you on your adventure. Collect more items to cast powerful attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ghosts of the Underworld</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/97ce8c92c7e21c8ce5c10e751794e0df.avif?t=1756972850\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras_big/97ce8c92c7e21c8ce5c10e751794e0df.avif?t=1756972850 width=800 height=332 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter ghosts with their own stories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game design considering replayability</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the underworld that changes every time you explore. Death is not the end. Explore and earn money to purchase reinforcements and items!!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hell Shooter</strong> is a roguelike dungeon crawler game. It features unique attack methods, exhilarating action, an oriental hellish atmosphere, and each character's storytelling.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique attack method</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/2eb5d15d29ce89807a39ff7d5163bd15.poster.avif?t=1756972850\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/2eb5d15d29ce89807a39ff7d5163bd15.webm?t=1756972850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/2eb5d15d29ce89807a39ff7d5163bd15.mp4?t=1756972850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When attacking enemies, you must only attack them by dashing!! Design the optimal attack path by bouncing between structures and enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Soul Eruption</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/96190dee2a2cf793494375854d8ddde2.poster.avif?t=1756972850\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/96190dee2a2cf793494375854d8ddde2.webm?t=1756972850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/96190dee2a2cf793494375854d8ddde2.mp4?t=1756972850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are rewards for good play. Collect the combo gauge to erupt your soul. It will be a powerful attack.</p><p cl